T1  - Research Notes. Distributive and Procedural Justice as Predictors of Satisfaction with Personal and Organizational Outcomes
AU  - McFarlin, Dean B.
AU  - Sweeney, Paul D.
Y1  - 1992/08/01
PY  - 1992
DA  - 1992/08/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/256489
